@page "/about"
<PageTitle>About AI Resume Scanner</PageTitle>

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h2>About AI Resume Scanner</h2>
    <p>
        The AI Resume Scanner is a smart tool designed to help recruiters and job seekers analyze resumes against specific job descriptions using artificial intelligence.
    </p>
    <h4>How the Process Works</h4>
    <ol class="mb-4">
        <li>
            <strong>Provide Job Description:</strong>
            Enter or paste the job description for the position you are hiring for.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Upload Resumes:</strong>
            Select and upload one or more resume files (PDF or Word format).
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>AI Analysis:</strong>
            The system uses Chat gpt model to compare each resume with the job description, evaluating how well each candidate matches the requirements.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Results & Insights:</strong>
            The scanner displays a summary for each resume, including tailoredness, match score, and evidence for matched requirements. You can view and download the analyzed resumes.
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p>
        This process streamlines candidate screening, making it easier to identify the best matches for your job openings.
    </p>
</div>
